14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. There is hereby appropriated to the J.D. McCarty
16 Center for Children with Developmental Disabilities from any monies
17 not otherwise appropriated from the Statewide Recovery Fund of the
18 State Treasury created in Section 255 of Title 62 of the Oklahoma
19 Statutes, the sum of Eight Hundred Thousand Dollars ($800,000.00) or
20 so much thereof as may be necessary to provide medical care for
21 children with developmental disabilities who are disproportionately
22 impacted by the pandemic. Such funds shall be utilized in a manner
23 consistent with the recommendations adopted by the Joint Committee
24 on Pandemic Relief Funding on May 12, 2025.
